    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/60318c8adf105b66350e8cb577d6ddd3.avif?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16Bit Survivors is a time survival game where spellcasting, darkness, and synergies are the main focus. Choose which spells you will use to burn, blast, freeze, and crackle the countless hordes of monsters with. Leave no creature breathing. Only the strongest builds will give you a chance to face each dungeon’s master. Good luck</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/b74fa043e4d487b6d8ddf35e030430a1.webp?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/6fee83bd80ceae5ac09f9aebcd745b1b.poster.avif?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/6fee83bd80ceae5ac09f9aebcd745b1b.webm?t=1736781852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/6fee83bd80ceae5ac09f9aebcd745b1b.mp4?t=1736781852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/3e62b730c43d181c1c67f3c7b83cc3fc.webp?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/1a817618cfd45f74aeab0930b95981b6.avif?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=64 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10min Runtime, Quick and Casual</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spellcasting: Aim with the mouse or controller to cast spells</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Darkness: Crawl through the shrouded dungeons to find secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monster Elites: Defeat stronger variations of monsters to earn meta-progressing currencies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heart Health System, collect hearts to grant special effects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/b74fa043e4d487b6d8ddf35e030430a1.webp?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/05accc8162e439c6bfeeec73bf8cc32a.poster.avif?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/05accc8162e439c6bfeeec73bf8cc32a.webm?t=1736781852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/05accc8162e439c6bfeeec73bf8cc32a.mp4?t=1736781852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/3e62b730c43d181c1c67f3c7b83cc3fc.webp?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=28 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Pixel Style Visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bit Crushed Audio bites for that delicious nostalgic sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Class Progression System; grow stronger with each run</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/b74fa043e4d487b6d8ddf35e030430a1.webp?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=28 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/9be291ad5fe57e2c50ba50c9a8bfbebf.poster.avif?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/9be291ad5fe57e2c50ba50c9a8bfbebf.webm?t=1736781852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/9be291ad5fe57e2c50ba50c9a8bfbebf.mp4?t=1736781852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210160/extras/3e62b730c43d181c1c67f3c7b83cc3fc.webp?t=1736781852\" width=640 height=28 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam Page Artists</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >XYEzawr - Pixel Art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CaptainSkeleto - Pixel Art</p></li></ul>",
